1
00:01:10,201 --> 00:01:11,909
I have some good news for you.

2
00:01:11,909 --> 00:01:12,734
What is it?

3
00:01:12,734 --> 00:01:16,734
Glamorous Airline is picking up Mr. Glam back to Thailand.

4
00:01:18,608 --> 00:01:19,962
It's been a tiring flight.

5
00:01:19,962 --> 00:01:21,598
Are you hungry?

6
00:01:21,598 --> 00:01:23,031
It's none of your business!

7
00:01:23,031 --> 00:01:25,031
Keep an eye on them, All-New.

8
00:01:27,581 --> 00:01:29,131
Mr. Glam, let us take you to a safe spot.

9
00:01:29,131 --> 00:01:30,763
Is this really about to turn into a murder scene?

10
00:01:30,763 --> 00:01:32,438
Mr. Glam got enemies?

11
00:01:32,438 --> 00:01:34,072
You, die!

12
00:01:34,072 --> 00:01:35,070
Did it really have to come to killing someone?

13
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:37,070
There is no other way.

14
00:02:10,026 --> 00:02:12,026
Madam Porn.

15
00:02:16,657 --> 00:02:18,007
Please don't harm me.

16
00:02:18,359 --> 00:02:20,072
I mean no harm. Please leave me alone.

17
00:02:20,072 --> 00:02:21,906
I'm not a ghost.

18
00:02:22,855 --> 00:02:23,884
Then, what the hell are you?

19
00:02:23,884 --> 00:02:25,237
Why are your eyes bleeding?

20
00:02:25,237 --> 00:02:27,190
No, it's my mascara.

21
00:02:27,698 --> 00:02:30,254
Why didn't you use a waterproof one?

22
00:02:30,254 --> 00:02:31,254
Shit.

23
00:02:32,127 --> 00:02:36,037
Oh, it's alright. Stop dancing first.

24
00:02:36,037 --> 00:02:38,790
That's a dancer we hired to pay respect after making a vow.

25
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:41,106
Why didn't you tell me first?

26
00:02:41,534 --> 00:02:44,770
But what vow did you make? I wanna know about that.

27
00:02:44,770 --> 00:02:45,323
That's my business.

28
00:02:45,323 --> 00:02:46,960
Yes, Madam.

29
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,276
I heard you won a lotto.

30
00:02:48,276 --> 00:02:49,984
That's fantastic, Madam.

31
00:02:49,984 --> 00:02:52,100
You hired a dancer and paid full respect to the spirits,
that must have cost more than ten thousand of Baht.

32
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:54,100
So you won a hundred thousand of Baht?

33
00:02:55,211 --> 00:02:57,211
No, it was two thousand Baht.

34
00:02:58,045 --> 00:02:59,756
That's why we're about to be out of business.

35
00:02:59,756 --> 00:03:00,756
I heard that!

36
00:03:01,906 --> 00:03:05,183
I just wanted to do something good for Father.

37
00:03:05,183 --> 00:03:08,093
Just hoping it'll bring some good into my life.

38
00:03:08,093 --> 00:03:09,486
Oh, right!

39
00:03:09,486 --> 00:03:11,234
I have some good news for you.

40
00:03:11,234 --> 00:03:12,272
What is it?

41
00:03:12,272 --> 00:03:13,984
Glamorous Airline...

42
00:03:13,984 --> 00:03:16,340
is picking up Mr. Glam back to Thailand.

43
00:03:16,340 --> 00:03:18,856
See? I told you!

44
00:03:18,856 --> 00:03:21,331
This is the blessng I got from making merit.

45
00:03:21,331 --> 00:03:23,809
Father has shown me mercy.

46
00:03:23,809 --> 00:03:26,124
Miss, keep on dancing,

47
00:03:26,124 --> 00:03:28,721
See? This is a good chance.

48
00:03:28,721 --> 00:03:31,395
You two will get closer to Glam.

49
00:03:31,395 --> 00:03:33,988
And you will find out his secrets.

50
00:03:33,988 --> 00:03:36,381
Oh, aside from good news...

51
00:03:36,381 --> 00:03:38,173
we also have bad news.

52
00:03:38,173 --> 00:03:39,448
What?

53
00:03:39,448 --> 00:03:41,485
This flight...

54
00:03:41,485 --> 00:03:43,198
trainees likes us...

55
00:03:43,198 --> 00:03:44,910
won't get to fly on Mr. Glam's flight.

56
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:47,026
Miss, stop the dance.

57
00:03:47,026 --> 00:03:49,258
Wait, that can't be happening.

58
00:03:49,258 --> 00:03:51,493
You guys have no other choice.

59
00:03:51,493 --> 00:03:53,968
You two must find a way to fly this flight.

60
00:03:53,968 --> 00:03:55,203
It's our golden chance.

61
00:03:55,203 --> 00:03:57,203
You must not miss this chance.

62
00:03:59,757 --> 00:04:01,197
That, I have handled it.

63
00:04:01,197 --> 00:04:02,911
Wait, what?

64
00:04:02,911 --> 00:04:05,385
I wanted to surprise you too.

65
00:04:05,385 --> 00:04:06,816
Hey, you did a great job, All-New!

66
00:04:06,816 --> 00:04:09,811
See? Father really has shown me mercy.

67
00:04:09,811 --> 00:04:12,285
Miss, continue dancing.

68
00:04:12,285 --> 00:04:13,444
You're superstitious.

69
00:04:13,444 --> 00:04:15,195
I heard that!

70
00:04:15,195 --> 00:04:16,823
Er, I said...

71
00:04:16,823 --> 00:04:20,823
that must be it! Father has shown us mercy.

72
00:04:21,213 --> 00:04:23,486
Now, that damn Glam...

73
00:04:23,486 --> 00:04:27,487
I'll get to know all of your secrets!

74
00:04:48,161 --> 00:04:48,997
Gift!

75
00:04:48,997 --> 00:04:49,510
What?

76
00:04:49,510 --> 00:04:50,901
I don't think you should go.

77
00:04:50,901 --> 00:04:52,570
Well, I want to see Mr. Glam.

78
00:04:52,570 --> 00:04:53,963
Why are you guys fighting?

79
00:04:53,963 --> 00:04:54,831
I'll go for you all.

80
00:04:54,831 --> 00:04:57,267
Don't be nosey. You, stay here!

81
00:04:57,737 --> 00:04:59,011
I'm going. I want to go. That'll be me...

82
00:04:59,011 --> 00:05:00,002
No, I'm going.

83
00:05:00,002 --> 00:05:01,837
I'm going. I'm begging you.

84
00:05:01,837 --> 00:05:02,951
No.

85
00:05:02,951 --> 00:05:03,386
I'm going.

86
00:05:03,386 --> 00:05:03,940
I am!

87
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:05,489
Guys, guys!

88
00:05:05,489 --> 00:05:07,885
It's that time you all have been waiting for...

89
00:05:07,885 --> 00:05:09,885
who will get to fly on Mr. Glam's flight...

90
00:05:11,559 --> 00:05:12,276
What?

91
00:05:12,276 --> 00:05:12,983
A lucky draw?

92
00:05:12,983 --> 00:05:15,573
Yes, so let this decide...

93
00:05:15,573 --> 00:05:17,924
whoever picks the green one...

94
00:05:17,924 --> 00:05:19,924
gets to go!

95
00:05:21,321 --> 00:05:23,707
That's fair. I'm always lucky.

96
00:05:23,707 --> 00:05:25,707
Tid-Gift, you go first.

97
00:05:28,702 --> 00:05:29,261
Hey!

98
00:05:29,261 --> 00:05:29,976
Why don't you get on a couch?

99
00:05:29,976 --> 00:05:30,853
No!

100
00:05:30,853 --> 00:05:31,853
C'mon!

101
00:05:37,049 --> 00:05:40,084
Oh my god, oh my god, oh my god...

102
00:05:40,084 --> 00:05:44,084
I get to go see Mr. Glam!

103
00:05:45,676 --> 00:05:47,154
Alright, next...c'mon!

104
00:05:47,154 --> 00:05:49,265
Me, me, me!

105
00:05:49,265 --> 00:05:50,015
Me too!

106
00:05:50,015 --> 00:05:51,644
You! Your hand!

107
00:05:51,644 --> 00:05:53,644
Sky, my pinky's torn now!

108
00:05:56,476 --> 00:05:59,385
See? Tid-Gift!

109
00:06:05,143 --> 00:06:05,777
Sky!

110
00:06:05,777 --> 00:06:07,136
I got the green one too!

111
00:06:07,136 --> 00:06:09,136
How about me? I get to go too, right?

112
00:06:11,693 --> 00:06:12,962
Not yet, c'mon.

113
00:06:12,962 --> 00:06:14,962
Wait, I can't lose my hand before I go take care of Mr. Glam.

114
00:06:17,395 --> 00:06:20,830
So many green ones! I get to go alone!

115
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:22,067
What's all this, Chai?

116
00:06:22,067 --> 00:06:23,024
Well, green means go.

117
00:06:23,024 --> 00:06:24,932
If you get them, you're in!

118
00:06:24,932 --> 00:06:27,007
That means we all get to go?

119
00:06:27,007 --> 00:06:28,717
Yes, we all get to go!

120
00:06:28,717 --> 00:06:30,074
Yes!

121
00:06:30,074 --> 00:06:31,108
I'm so happy.

122
00:06:31,108 --> 00:06:33,146
Wait, Kreetha and All-New get to go too?

123
00:06:33,146 --> 00:06:33,934
Yes.

124
00:06:33,934 --> 00:06:35,485
Then...

125
00:06:35,485 --> 00:06:37,397
why bother with the draw if everyone's going anyway?

126
00:06:37,397 --> 00:06:40,430
I like it...it gives me a thrill.

127
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:41,430
Oh.

128
00:06:43,020 --> 00:06:44,098
Oh, that was tiring and it was all for nothing.

129
00:06:44,098 --> 00:06:45,098
Right! What's the point?

130
00:06:45,892 --> 00:06:46,964
We all get to go, that's one thing.

131
00:06:46,964 --> 00:06:48,832
But we all gotta prepare ourselves.

132
00:06:48,832 --> 00:06:52,823
Because this trip is extraordinary. Be ready.

133
00:06:52,823 --> 00:06:53,823
Okay.

134
00:06:59,132 --> 00:07:00,363
Wait, Chaba.

135
00:07:00,363 --> 00:07:01,437
We're flying tomorrow.

136
00:07:01,437 --> 00:07:02,954
You're getting ready now?

137
00:07:02,954 --> 00:07:04,825
I just put on some lipstick.

138
00:07:04,825 --> 00:07:05,825
Take a look at that.

139
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:12,500
This is nothing. Take a look at that.

140
00:07:14,971 --> 00:07:15,971
Hey!

141
00:07:16,767 --> 00:07:17,767
Sky!

142
00:07:18,161 --> 00:07:20,268
Are you gonna offer yourself to him or something?

143
00:07:20,268 --> 00:07:22,268
Right, are you gonna be his wife or something?

144
00:07:23,022 --> 00:07:24,022
Of course!

145
00:07:24,458 --> 00:07:27,774
What if one day I end up with Mr. Glam?

146
00:07:27,774 --> 00:07:29,804
I'll get to be Mrs. Glam.

147
00:07:29,804 --> 00:07:31,515
I won't let you guys fly.

148
00:07:31,515 --> 00:07:35,515
I'll let you all be my servants. How does that sound?

149
00:07:36,104 --> 00:07:37,337
You're not Mrs. Glam yet...

150
00:07:37,337 --> 00:07:41,337
and you already have people washing your face now?

151
00:07:42,252 --> 00:07:43,361
That's my feet.

152
00:07:43,361 --> 00:07:44,361
Well, I can't tell the difference.

153
00:07:50,193 --> 00:07:51,193
Ooh, that's yummy.

154
00:07:56,184 --> 00:07:58,974
I'm pretty excited about meeting Mr. Glam.

155
00:07:58,974 --> 00:07:59,974
That's true.

156
00:08:01,203 --> 00:08:02,598
This only happens every once in a while.

157
00:08:02,598 --> 00:08:03,598
That's true.

158
00:08:04,907 --> 00:08:07,380
Where the hell is Sky?

159
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:08,855
She went to the restroom but that was quite a while ago.

160
00:08:08,855 --> 00:08:10,855
Maybe she's not confident about her looks.

161
00:08:12,053 --> 00:08:13,053
Mabuhay!

162
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,837
What's gotten into you?

163
00:08:17,837 --> 00:08:19,837
Sky, is that a mosquito spray?

164
00:08:21,698 --> 00:08:24,689
This is my latest perfume.

165
00:08:24,689 --> 00:08:25,597
And that's not all.

166
00:08:25,597 --> 00:08:27,597
Fresh breath is important.

167
00:08:29,387 --> 00:08:31,904
Whoa, are you not gonna be a flight attendant anymore?

168
00:08:31,904 --> 00:08:33,696
You're thinking about owning this airline now?

169
00:08:33,696 --> 00:08:35,410
Absolutely.

170
00:08:35,410 --> 00:08:38,801
Mr. Glam is going to be our passenger today.

171
00:08:38,801 --> 00:08:43,801
He's handsome, rich and most importantly, he's single.

172
00:08:44,906 --> 00:08:48,574
So this is my only chance to be Mrs. Glam.

173
00:08:48,574 --> 00:08:51,927
I'm not gonna be an exhausted flight attendant like you two any longer.

174
00:08:51,927 --> 00:08:52,927
Go ahead.

175
00:08:54,319 --> 00:08:56,874
Guys, Chai...

176
00:08:58,746 --> 00:09:00,623
Whoa!

177
00:09:00,623 --> 00:09:02,733
Who used a toilet spray?

178
00:09:02,733 --> 00:09:04,081
Er, that's perfume.

179
00:09:04,081 --> 00:09:05,081
Oh.

180
00:09:05,395 --> 00:09:08,187
Are you going to a funeral?

181
00:09:08,187 --> 00:09:09,739
I'm not going to a funeral.

182
00:09:09,739 --> 00:09:11,739
I'm going to knock down a beehive.

183
00:09:14,250 --> 00:09:15,250
Way to ruin my self-esteem.

184
00:09:15,717 --> 00:09:17,717
Er...I think you might as well take off your gloves.

185
00:09:19,105 --> 00:09:20,653
Oh, right! Chai told me to come get you guys.

186
00:09:20,653 --> 00:09:22,726
Mr. Glam is expecting you all outside.

187
00:09:22,726 --> 00:09:23,565
Are you ready?

188
00:09:23,565 --> 00:09:24,565
We're ready.

189
00:09:28,952 --> 00:09:29,952
Today, it's one of us...

190
00:09:31,304 --> 00:09:32,304
Go ahead.

191
00:09:34,732 --> 00:09:37,041
Ohm, I humbly summon all the Rishis, the trio of Divine Sages.

192
00:09:37,041 --> 00:09:39,559
Sage Fire-Eye, Sage Wide-Eyes, and Sage Yellow-Toothed Yam-Eater.

193
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:42,395
Yes, he got yellow teeth becauses he ate yam.

194
00:09:42,395 --> 00:09:44,787
May he love me. May he adore me.

195
00:09:44,787 --> 00:09:47,696
Sky, I heard all of that!

196
00:09:47,696 --> 00:09:50,087
You're superstitious. Did the Rishis get on the plane too?

197
00:09:50,087 --> 00:09:51,123
I just did a little prayer.

198
00:09:51,123 --> 00:09:52,431
Don't. Not a word.

199
00:09:52,431 --> 00:09:53,385
We're adorable.

200
00:09:53,864 --> 00:09:55,864
We're really adorable. You go ahead.

201
00:09:57,017 --> 00:09:59,017
That was nonsense.

202
00:09:59,534 --> 00:10:04,846
Namo, oh might Rishis of the Radiant Eyes...

203
00:10:04,846 --> 00:10:05,796
Pink-Eyed Sage,

204
00:10:05,796 --> 00:10:06,989
Sky-Blue-Eyed Sage,

205
00:10:06,989 --> 00:10:08,896
Yellowish-Orange-Eyed Sage,

206
00:10:08,896 --> 00:10:10,094
and the One with a Hint of Navy...

207
00:10:10,094 --> 00:10:11,167
Let Mr. Glam...

208
00:10:11,167 --> 00:10:12,167
be...

209
00:10:12,797 --> 00:10:14,226
Are your Rishis queer?

210
00:10:14,733 --> 00:10:15,406
Well, they've been helping me a lot.

211
00:10:15,406 --> 00:10:17,406
You're unbelievable.

212
00:10:32,038 --> 00:10:36,038
I'd like to introduce the crew that will be taking care of you, Mr. Glam.

213
00:10:40,071 --> 00:10:40,505
Wait, hang on a sec.

214
00:10:40,505 --> 00:10:41,136
Yes, sir.

215
00:10:41,136 --> 00:10:42,732
Let my dog out for a run first.

216
00:10:42,732 --> 00:10:43,843
She wants to pee.

217
00:10:43,843 --> 00:10:44,272
Of course.

218
00:10:44,272 --> 00:10:45,388
Can a dog pee on this plane?

219
00:10:45,388 --> 00:10:47,180
Yes, sir. Anywhere on the plane.

220
00:10:47,180 --> 00:10:48,454
Go ahead, dear.

221
00:10:48,454 --> 00:10:49,252
Poop for me too.

222
00:10:49,252 --> 00:10:52,724
Why don't we let her go so I can introduce the crew?

223
00:10:54,511 --> 00:10:56,264
I don't think you should do that just yet.

224
00:10:56,264 --> 00:10:58,173
From what I see...

225
00:10:58,173 --> 00:11:00,173
you all aren't ready.

226
00:11:03,161 --> 00:11:07,161
You lack discipline, I can see it from how you're standing.

227
00:11:08,992 --> 00:11:10,630
May I?

228
00:11:10,630 --> 00:11:14,630
Mr. Handsome, scoot over to the left a bit.

229
00:11:15,785 --> 00:11:16,455
Yes, sir.

230
00:11:16,455 --> 00:11:17,455
That's enough.

231
00:11:17,773 --> 00:11:19,773
Mr. Glasses, you too.

232
00:11:22,921 --> 00:11:24,921
Step out of my cowhide rug.

233
00:11:26,036 --> 00:11:29,028
And you...

234
00:11:29,458 --> 00:11:33,457
I guess that's why we've gone through so much turbulence.

235
00:11:33,490 --> 00:11:35,366
You don't have to walk or serve anything today.

236
00:11:35,366 --> 00:11:37,366
Slide over just a bit.

237
00:11:38,917 --> 00:11:41,068
No, you stay there.

238
00:11:41,068 --> 00:11:42,339
Step aside just a little.

239
00:11:42,339 --> 00:11:44,339
I don't want you to be too close to me.

240
00:11:45,529 --> 00:11:49,517
And for you...

241
00:11:49,517 --> 00:11:50,517
May I...

242
00:11:54,113 --> 00:11:55,113
A little bit to the right...

243
00:12:00,108 --> 00:12:01,108
That's perfect.

244
00:12:02,264 --> 00:12:04,573
Okay, so if it's all perfect now...

245
00:12:04,573 --> 00:12:06,282
and nothing is missing...

246
00:12:06,282 --> 00:12:07,078
Yes.

247
00:12:07,078 --> 00:12:11,077
Wait, is there anything else you're not happy with?

248
00:12:12,629 --> 00:12:15,064
I don't think so.

249
00:12:15,064 --> 00:12:19,063
I think I've found what makes me happy.

250
00:12:26,769 --> 00:12:28,560
If you're happy with everything...

251
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:29,233
Yes.

252
00:12:29,233 --> 00:12:31,710
I'd like to officially introduce the crew.

253
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:32,710
Yes.

254
00:12:34,698 --> 00:12:36,771
Let's start with...

255
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:39,040
My name is Kree...

256
00:12:40,273 --> 00:12:41,470
It's Kreetha. Kreetha.

257
00:12:41,470 --> 00:12:42,782
Oh, Kreetha.

258
00:12:42,782 --> 00:12:44,657
Yes.

259
00:12:44,657 --> 00:12:45,057
All-New.

260
00:12:45,448 --> 00:12:45,848
All-New.

261
00:12:46,237 --> 00:12:47,350
V16.

262
00:12:47,350 --> 00:12:47,907
Wow.

263
00:12:47,907 --> 00:12:48,901
1,100 horsepower.

264
00:12:48,901 --> 00:12:49,854
The ultimate tough-blooded pickup.

265
00:12:49,854 --> 00:12:50,610
Yes.

266
00:12:50,610 --> 00:12:51,798
This is the one that beat Tesla?

267
00:12:51,798 --> 00:12:53,229
Of course.

268
00:12:53,229 --> 00:12:54,503
Nice to meet you.

269
00:12:54,503 --> 00:12:55,020
Hello.

270
00:12:55,020 --> 00:12:55,854
I'm Chaba.

271
00:12:55,854 --> 00:12:56,893
Chaba...

272
00:12:56,893 --> 00:12:59,008
Wow, you're blooming.

273
00:12:59,008 --> 00:13:00,008
Indeed.

274
00:13:01,201 --> 00:13:01,875
Hello, I'm Sky.

275
